{"tid":1322330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"意大利警方搜查極右組織檢獲導彈和軍火","createTime":"2019-07-16T02:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T02:27:35.000Z","uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e1ffee4e39794d1b69adde5111def49988693831","tid":1322330,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T02:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1468561_1_20190716015819.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1468561_1_20190716015819.jpg&h=c11387c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n意大利反恐警方在一個機庫，搜出一支空對空導彈。（美聯社）<br />\n \t<br />\n鄧詠盈報道<br />\n意大利反恐警方在北部突擊搜查極右組織時，檢獲一支導彈和大批武器，拘捕3人。<br />\n<br />\n警方說，該支法國製空對空導彈在一個機場的機庫搜出，性能良好，屬卡塔爾軍方使用，相信被捕人士意圖把導彈出售。<br />\n<br />\n其他武器包括自動步槍、火箭發射器、手槍、刺刀、彈藥和有納粹標誌的物品。<br />\n<br />\n今次行動是針對意大利極右組織，協助烏克蘭東部親俄分離分子作戰的調查工作一部分。<br />\n<br />\n被捕3人介乎42至51歲，包括一名瑞士人和兩名意大利人，其中一個是前海關人員，是一個極右政黨的活躍分子，曾經在2001年參加參議院選舉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468561-20190716.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468561-20190716.htm&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=6a392141\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468561-20190716.htm&h=c4f8bb9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468561-20190716.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6665c4b1b8f257ca4cea44b5aaac605d7f762809","tid":1322330,"uid":91721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T02:10:18.000Z","msg":"喺香港<br />\n則有環保倉當武器庫"},{"pid":"ba5f0238ba346e33bfacabb7b0fa20802a4838ce","tid":1322330,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T02:27:35.000Z","msg":"Air to air係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無飛機點射"}]}